{"tid":1645394,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"Learnt Helplessness","createTime":"2019-10-11T01:11:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-11T01:11:59.000Z","uid":330966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f8d8c36b2471e722c8ea1699905de7c41524a4cb","tid":1645394,"uid":330966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-11T01:11:59.000Z","msg":"琴日特登出去撐場&hellip; 我想講好少好少好好少人&hellip;&hellip;少得好可憐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過最近我稔發生既事太多，大家可能消化唔到，但唔希望大家係唔堅持，選擇棄守<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 琴晚中大又有新屋嶺被捕人士出聲，之後HKPF FB又回應，個女仔咁勇敢，大家呢？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />仲有！！見大家宜排係咁屌人唔行動，態度可唔可以溫柔少少？ 我地<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: purple;\">不分化 不割蓆 </span></strong></span><br />\n大家就咁鐘意屌自己人咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔係個個都受宜套<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁講講&hellip; 讀psycho既我好擔心宜家政府玩既策略叫 Learnt Helplessness<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/W3f9AwW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FW3f9AwW.jpg&h=83dad048&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n習得性無助現象在人類和動物身上都可以觀察到。當他們條件反射式地預期自己將會遭受痛苦、折磨並且認為自己對此無能為力時，就會產生習得性無助(Cherry, 2017)。經過反覆多次的「條件化」，個體習得某種信念--「無論做何努力都無法改變現狀或未來時」，人/動物將會放棄抵抗和努力，停止擺脫痛苦或惡劣情境的嘗試--即使他們有機會！<br />\n<br />\n大家要有宜家意識 去搵岩自己既方法幫助自己 <br />\n一有&ldquo;做咩都無用 變唔到&rdquo;宜個稔法就好危險～"}]}